RelicOfConvergence: {
	DisplayName: Relic of Convergence
	Tooltip:
		'''
		Creates a profaned crystal at the cursor that channels a healing aura before shattering
		All players within the area of effect are healed for {0} HP
		Allies gain 50% extra healing
		Holding out the crystal reduces the damage of all summons, decreases defense, and increases incoming damage
		[c/FF8C00:Never once had I known kindness. Neither my peers or family had a shred of compassion for me.]
		[c/FF8C00:I wished for someone I could confide. A presence that cleansed me of anxiety.]
		[c/FF8C00:And when I saw Her radiant smile when we met, I knew I had finally found it.]
		'''
}

RelicOfResilience: {
	DisplayName: Relic of Resilience
	Tooltip:
		'''
		Holding this item creates orbiting rock shards around you and nearby allies
		After 5 seconds, the relic will retain orbiting rocks even when not holding the item
		Continuing to hold the item will steadily increase the number of rocks and defenses until reaching max power
		While they orbit you, your minimum defense is set to 200 and minimum damage reduction to 10%
		Taking a hit or pressing <right> while holding this item will pull in the shards, then blast them outward, crippling hit enemies
		This effect has a 10 second cooldown after taking a hit, but recharges faster if holding the item
		Holding out the shield heavily reduces the damage of all summons
		[c/FF8C00:I saw a massacre and did nothing to stop it. My vow broken, I was shunned.]
		[c/FF8C00:My will to forge ahead vanished. My final wish was simply to not die alone.]
		[c/FF8C00:But when She put faith in my shield, I would never again let it falter.]
		'''
}

